Software Design: High Level Algorithm
Display on
Auto on
Check for button push -- Sense button 
       If button is pushed, then SVC POT
       ELSE, SVC AUTO
POT: 
Turn auto off
Read POT
Display POT value
Go to Control
AUTO:
Turn auto on
Set Comfy Zone Value (set point)
Go to Control
CONTROL:
Measure room_ temp
Compare room_temp  to setpoint or pot value
       If room_temp = setpoint Â± 3
               Check again (POLL)
       Else if room_temp > setpoint + 3
               Turn on fan
               Turn off heater
               Return to CONTROL
       Else if room_temp < setpoint - 3
               Turn on heater
               Turn off fan
               Return to CONTROL

